title: Zdenek Štybar confirms his WorldTour road career is over
content:
The former cyclocross world champion won 18 races across his road racing career, including Strade Bianche, E3 Saxo Bank, and stages at the Tour de France and Vuelta a España.

Read the full article at Zdenek Štybar confirms his WorldTour road career is over on Velo.
author: ahood
